data.eml:eml: First record of Axinyssa Lendenfeld, 1897 (Demospongiae, Halichondrida) from the East Pacific Ocean, with the description of Axinyssa isabela sp. nov.

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Carballo, José Luis, Cruz-Barraza, José Antonio (2008): First record of Axinyssa Lendenfeld, 1897 (Demospongiae, Halichondrida) from the East Pacific Ocean, with the description of Axinyssa isabela sp. nov.
